Class CalTotal

  • java.lang.Object
    • calculations.CalTotal

  • public class CalTotal
extends java.lang.Object
    This class adds together the user's input of calories. The purpose of this class is to take from user input to combine all entries into a total. The user will input the calories they've consumed over a period of time (EX: During the user's average day) & this class will add them together and then display a total when prompted.
    Author:
    Spencer Keeton
